Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.36,0:00:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然相信敵人的話喪失戰鬥意志
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.18,0:00:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.09,0:00:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別輕易放棄生命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我的副官 就應該堅強一些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.96,0:00:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會繼續把背後交給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃一塹長一智
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐也說不了別人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令官居然擅自跑出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.87,0:00:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.91,0:00:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是和妳一個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.21,0:00:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說不應該是附帶美人護士的個人房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.33,0:00:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間在一起比較容易護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.01,0:00:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼他們不來殺我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼讓火焰之混蛋活著回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:00:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙可是把拉斯多活活燒死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯多死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也不遲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.51,0:01:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那傢伙殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.13,0:01:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅伊·馬斯坦古 可以利用他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道讓那傢伙把門…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.73,0:01:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人已經把他交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.28,0:02:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果腐爛了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那邊的肉體可沒有攝取營養
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使回到那種身體裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 溫莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…愛德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.02,0:03:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是假說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想鍊成媽媽的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為靈魂的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我和阿爾的血混進去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 我們一起被拉去了那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被分解了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在分解中 我和阿爾的精神混在了一起的可能性難道沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的我和在那邊的阿爾的肉體連在一起的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我這個年紀身高就這麼一…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承認了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對現實了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德同時在承受著阿爾的身體成長？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得是個離奇的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不離奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是因為不喝牛奶所以長不高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是牛奶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 哥哥經常在睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道也承受了我的睡眠時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs60}（說不要就不要）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\an8}（喝）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs60}（不要）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}愚者的前進
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去探望大佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈博克先生也受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想專門打聲招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果大佐沒有趕到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在都不知道變成什麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利曹長也是探病？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉的跑腿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從進入第三研究所的地下後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計算的步數推測
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測出了到那個大門為止的大概距離
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為方向不明確
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以以研究所為中心畫了一個圓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央司令部？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 這個建築物是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大總統官邸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造人們在建築物的地下？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大總統和他們串在一起的可能性也是有的…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果串在一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼大總統做掉了古利德一伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假設沒串在一起也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不逼問出任何情報就把他們全滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大總統
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人滲透了軍隊的高層
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後要小心對應
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼 要慎重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造人 大總統
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這獵物比預想得還要大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也感覺太過龐大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有幹的意義 挺不錯的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 你們可得給我拚命地幹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我暫時脫隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的雙腳 沒有感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我退出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體哪裡不舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查醫生必須長時間站著 年紀大了可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說燒了那個的是你 我突然想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在計劃些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我在計劃什麼卻斷定了那個是羅斯少尉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰友真是可貴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是戰友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是共犯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你燒 我解剖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修瓦爾曾變成了巨大的實驗場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險的事情幹多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會嘗到後果的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經嘗到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為脊髓損傷 下半身癱瘓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得得到了一天一根煙的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 被女人刺到退役真是笑死人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退役後準備怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家是做雜貨店的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接電話還是能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.94,0:07:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法做成機械鎧嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:08:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下半身整個的神經回路都斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不適合隱居生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈博克腳的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼之大將給的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬可醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精通醫療領域的鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢者之石？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的休假能延長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休假結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東部的旅行怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美人很多 是個好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在從憲兵司令部傳過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先傳達給國家鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是國家鍊金術師 立刻就讓我去參觀了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去地下的入口呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有用鍊金術堵上的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒笨到會留下入口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來從這裡去找人造人是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說我是珍貴的人柱 死了就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也被這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開過門的人能成為人柱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人柱大概就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開門後還回得來的 有能力的術師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們捧為人柱 到底想要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要從那些傢伙口中逼問出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德華君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普羅修軍曹？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上回酒店比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果希望的話 可以給你派護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憲兵司令部通告全市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡再次出現在中央都市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者3名 全部是國家鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他 負傷者多人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據目擊情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特徵是額頭上巨大的十字傷疤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另加右臂全部是刺青的伊修瓦爾人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右臂和刺青
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡殺了洛克貝爾的叔叔阿姨？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 不能對溫莉說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不想再看到那傢伙哭喪的臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再和斯卡對峙一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了確認真相？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是其中的一個原因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了引出人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我死了的話 他們會頭痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 如果我被斯卡襲擊陷入危機的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得幾率很低
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比什麼都不做要好一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們之前一瞬間就被斯卡做掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計我們比原先要強一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使人造人出現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼才能抓住他們？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但很厲害而且幾乎是不死之身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死之身？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是長生不老的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又從窗戶進來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們協助你們作戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:11:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對軍隊的事情沒有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是關於人造人和長生不老就不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺我被懷疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於救了羅斯少尉這件事要感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴多點總沒壞處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這關係我們一族的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可別帶著人造人跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會遵守約定的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有一飯之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一飯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是room service費？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.77,0:12:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這哪裡是一飯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要早起 這樣人家不是無法睡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 要回拉修巴雷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:12:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個取消吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在中央都市多待一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手臂也許會壞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是…會弄壞…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有弄壞的預定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的靈魂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別幹太多危險的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生 醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束手無策了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我母親和退役軍人局的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退役的手續辦完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒確認治不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒笨到連自己的身體如何都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要沒法動的棋子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔下我 捨棄我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還有空管我這個跑腿的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還有和休斯准將的約定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要你的同情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈博克少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:14:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔下你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會扔下你 所以你自己追上來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.49,0:15:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上面等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人都沒有捨棄放棄生存的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說把背後交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法捨棄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼天真怎麼可能爬到這個國家的最頂端
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想有一個這種笨蛋也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:15:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的軍服拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不是能出院的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你幹了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣今天只能休業了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你遇到麻煩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國家鍊金術師 愛德華·愛力克登場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害 孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮金要多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮金？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要 不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的罐子壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我修好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小事一件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德華·愛力克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個城市裡的國家鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是愛德華·愛力克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我修好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城裡都是我的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為幹得那麼誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做這些事情可不像你的風格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐？已經可以出院了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈博克少尉的事情我聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果馬可醫生的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太顯眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐上來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是下車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬可先生失蹤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能被他們擄走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事先放一放 鋼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡的事情聽說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹的事情不是在叫他找到你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想讓他找到我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須要和他再戰一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了在東方之都被整成什麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怕斯卡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為之前大佐殿下完全沒有起到任何作用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看不起人 今天可是大晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你怎麼全身都軟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說曹操曹操就到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 沒下雨卻全身濕透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 中尉 不能開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模仿大佐想要釣魚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.30,0:18:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥打算以自己為誘餌把人造人引出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為哥哥對他們來說是不能死掉的人柱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:18:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不想再有犧牲者了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我或者哥哥來做誘餌了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果人造人出來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡被憲兵射殺了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大佐會替我們搞定的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我當打下手的使喚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽子不小
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住人造人分我一份
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利軍曹的其他住宅就在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的兩位 請退下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開槍 會打到哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 如果斯卡被打中了 就全完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.57,0:19:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不抓住不離開 真是難
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒來嗎 人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:19:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憲兵司令部的頻道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是菲利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是第3區憲兵隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在和斯卡交戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求緊急支援
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 下面是17區
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.85,0:20:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17區也出現了斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼3區的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達古拉斯大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8區也出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央憲兵隊發至第8區
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡和少年交戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年是國家鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤報橫飛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 第四個斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.73,0:20:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是第3區 沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是第8區 發現斯卡 請求緊急支援
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.09,0:20:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞到了 聞到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個伊修瓦爾人的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.51,0:21:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這氣息是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到了嗎 蘭芳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.91,0:21:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪個 是人體破壞還是機械鎧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用分解能量相互抵消？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.57,0:21:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右臂的刺青
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋 果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.63,0:21:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞到了 聞到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體可真奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面有幾個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.47,0:21:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.90,0:21:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那獨特的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管逃去哪裡 我都能追上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人 敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.83,0:22:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能吃掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.62,0:22:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 能發覺氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.84,0:22:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是礙事的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排除
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.91,0:22:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭芳 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.64,0:22:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭芳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被斬的少女所發出的悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中央都市迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.38,0:24:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹂躪的力量在和過去邂逅之時
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.07,0:24:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將喚醒暴力的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.25,0:24:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.01,0:24:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.71,0:24:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第22話 遠方的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.28,0:24:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要守護
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.83,0:24:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年如此想著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.88,0:01:26.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}純白的景色在向我招手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:32.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur4}我即將起程   前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:41.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}迷茫的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.74,0:01:44.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:50.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在不斷變化的地圖裡 攙雜著各種夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:52.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:57.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}即使以我這微小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:02:03.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}也能走到那雲的彼端嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:04.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}故作堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:06.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}卻受了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:09.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}彷彿看透了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:10.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}從天上落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.89,0:02:13.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}點點雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:16.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}反復的漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:19.17,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}筆直的光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:21.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}相互交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:25.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}並不知道去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:26.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}只管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:28.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}不停地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:34.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}淡淡的殘影烙印在兩眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:36.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}在這片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:39.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}無論身在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:42.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}一定可以到達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:47.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}那未曾見過的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.59,0:22:33.30,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fsp-1.5\fnRoman\fs35\b1}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.30,0:22:37.37,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}不必故作堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.63,0:22:44.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人這樣描繪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:49.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在牆上塗鴉的花也會搖動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.95,0:22:55.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人知道真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.55,0:22:57.86,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在漫長的路途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:01.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去與獲取
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:08.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}突然寂寞  也有哭泣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.02,0:23:16.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚也好  痛苦也好  都將化為恆星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:22.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點燃照亮明天的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:27.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉起小手  兩個人一起創造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:32.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去搜尋星塵與光芒四射的永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:38.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 那天也許還會降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.17,0:23:44.11,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}即使季節依然在不斷地交替
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.45,0:23:48.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有點迷茫  也要向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.19,0:23:52.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.23,0:23:56.54,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}請讓我維持到永遠


